			</div> 

			<div id="browser" class="section">
				<h2 class="subtitle">Browser support</h2>
				<p>Works in all modern browsers. (IE10+, Chrome, Firefox, Safari).</p>
				<p>Gracefully degrades in IE9. (Requires Modernizr).</p>
				<p>Not yet tested on Windows Phone.</p>	
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>   
